<TITLE> Minor nabbed in possession of grenade </TITLE>
<TEXT>
 Naogaon, Apr 11 (bdnews24.com)Police have arrested a teenager in possession of a grenade on Sunday. Officer in charge of the Nagaon Sadr Police Station, Aminul Islam, told bdnews24.com that the 15-year old was arrested from the polytechnic institute area in the afternoon. Aminul said that the police was investigating whether Mahbubul Alam Caeser was involved with any militant organisation. They are also trying to ascertain whether the grenade might have been used in some terrorist activity, he added. The 15-year old Mahbubul hails from Chakpathuria village under the sadr upazila and is the son of one Altaf Hossain. bdnews2
